  <entry>
    <title>vhdl2 时序电路基础</title>
    <url>/2020/08/04/vhdl2%20%E6%97%B6%E5%BA%8F%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>用 VHDL 语言设计实现一个分频系数为10，分频输出信号占空比为 50 的分频器，仿真并且验证其功能。</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight vhdl"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">LIBRARY</span> IEEE;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">USE</span> IEEE.STD_LOGIC_1164.<span class="keyword">ALL</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ENTITY</span> divider <span class="keyword">IS</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">PORT</span>(clk: <span class="keyword">IN</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC</span>;</span><br><span class="line">         clken: <span class="keyword">IN</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC</span>; <span class="comment">--clken=1 reset</span></span><br><span class="line">         clk2: <span class="keyword">OUT</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">END</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ARCHITECTURE</span> divider <span class="keyword">of</span> divider <span class="keyword">IS</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">signal</span> temp: <span class="built_in">INTEGER</span> <span class="keyword">RANGE</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">TO</span> <span class="number">9</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">BEGIN</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">process</span>(clk,temp)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">begin</span> </span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span>(clken=<span class="string">'1'</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">			temp&lt;=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">elsif</span>(clk<span class="symbol">'event</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> clk=<span class="string">'1'</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span>(temp=<span class="number">9</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">				temp&lt;=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">				temp&lt;=temp+<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		 <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">process</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">process</span>(clk,temp)</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">begin</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">if</span>(temp&lt;<span class="number">5</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">              clk2&lt;=<span class="string">'0'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">              clk2&lt;=<span class="string">'1'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">process</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://md.byr.moe/uploads/upload_5885d67bce5e20cb8e1a5867af09ac39.png" alt=""></p>
<ul>
<li>8421十进制计数器</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight vhdl"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">LIBRARY</span> IEEE;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">USE</span> IEEE.STD_LOGIC_1164.<span class="keyword">ALL</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">USE</span> IEEE.STD_LOGIC_UNSIGNED.<span class="keyword">ALL</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ENTITY</span> counter <span class="keyword">IS</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">PORT</span>(clk:<span class="keyword">IN</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        load: <span class="keyword">IN</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        din: <span class="keyword">IN</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC_VECTOR</span>(<span class="number">3</span> <span class="keyword">downto</span> <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        qout: <span class="keyword">OUT</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC_VECTOR</span>(<span class="number">3</span> <span class="keyword">downto</span> <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        c: <span class="keyword">OUT</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">END</span> counter;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ARCHITECTURE</span> counter <span class="keyword">of</span> counter <span class="keyword">IS</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SIGNAL</span> temp:<span class="built_in">std_logic_vector</span>(<span class="number">3</span> <span class="keyword">downto</span> <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">BEGIN</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">process</span>(clk,load,din)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">begin</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(load=<span class="string">'0'</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">            temp&lt;=din;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">elsif</span>(clk<span class="symbol">'event</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> clk=<span class="string">'1'</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">           	<span class="keyword">if</span>(temp=<span class="string">"1001"</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">                temp&lt;=<span class="string">"0000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">                temp&lt;=temp+<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">process</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       qout&lt;=temp;</span><br><span class="line">       c&lt;=<span class="string">'1'</span> <span class="keyword">when</span> temp=<span class="string">"1001"</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="string">'0'</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">END</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://md.byr.moe/uploads/upload_e32fb79eef754d9b072e62327000e15d.png" alt=""></p>
<ul>
<li>将分频器，十进制计数器和数码管译码器3个电路进行连接</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight vhdl"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">LIBRARY</span> IEEE;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">USE</span> IEEE.STD_LOGIC_1164.<span class="keyword">ALL</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">USE</span> IEEE.STD_LOGIC_UNSIGNED.<span class="keyword">ALL</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ENTITY</span> ledshow <span class="keyword">IS</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">PORT</span>(clk: <span class="keyword">IN</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC</span>;</span><br><span class="line">         aout:<span class="keyword">OUT</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC_VECTOR</span>(<span class="number">7</span> <span class="keyword">downto</span> <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">         load:<span class="keyword">IN</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC</span>;</span><br><span class="line">         din:<span class="keyword">IN</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC_VECTOR</span>(<span class="number">3</span> <span class="keyword">downto</span> <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        );</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">END</span> ledshow;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ARCHITECTURE</span> ledshow <span class="keyword">of</span> ledshow <span class="keyword">IS</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">signal</span> clk2:<span class="built_in">std_logic</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">signal</span> ctemp:<span class="built_in">integer</span> <span class="keyword">range</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">to</span> <span class="number">4999</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">signal</span> qtemp:<span class="built_in">std_logic_vector</span>(<span class="number">3</span> <span class="keyword">downto</span> <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">signal</span> qout:<span class="built_in">std_logic_vector</span>(<span class="number">3</span> <span class="keyword">downto</span> <span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">begin</span></span><br><span class="line">divider:<span class="keyword">process</span>(clk,ctemp)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">begin</span> </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(clk<span class="symbol">'event</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> clk=<span class="string">'1'</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(ctemp=<span class="number">4999</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">                ctemp&lt;=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">                ctemp&lt;=ctemp+<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">process</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">process</span>(clk,ctemp)</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">begin</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">if</span>(ctemp&lt;=<span class="number">2500</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">              clk2&lt;=<span class="string">'0'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">              clk2&lt;=<span class="string">'1'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">process</span>;</span><br><span class="line">counter:<span class="keyword">process</span>(clk2,load,din)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">begin</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(load=<span class="string">'0'</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">            qtemp&lt;=din;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">elsif</span>(clk2<span class="symbol">'event</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> clk2=<span class="string">'1'</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">           	<span class="keyword">if</span>(qtemp=<span class="string">"1001"</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">                qtemp&lt;=<span class="string">"0000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">                qtemp&lt;=qtemp+<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">process</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       qout&lt;=qtemp;</span><br><span class="line">       aout&lt;=<span class="string">"1111110"</span> <span class="keyword">when</span> qout=<span class="string">"0000"</span> <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">		   <span class="string">"0001100"</span> <span class="keyword">when</span> qout=<span class="string">"0001"</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> </span><br><span class="line">		   <span class="string">"1101101"</span> <span class="keyword">when</span> qout=<span class="string">"0010"</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> </span><br><span class="line">		   <span class="string">"1111001"</span> <span class="keyword">when</span> qout=<span class="string">"0011"</span> <span class="keyword">else</span>            </span><br><span class="line">		   <span class="string">"0110011"</span> <span class="keyword">when</span> qout=<span class="string">"0100"</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> </span><br><span class="line">		   <span class="string">"1011011"</span> <span class="keyword">when</span> qout=<span class="string">"0101"</span> <span class="keyword">else</span>   </span><br><span class="line">		   <span class="string">"0011111"</span> <span class="keyword">when</span> qout=<span class="string">"0110"</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> </span><br><span class="line">		   <span class="string">"1110000"</span> <span class="keyword">when</span> qout=<span class="string">"0111"</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> </span><br><span class="line">		   <span class="string">"1111111"</span> <span class="keyword">when</span> qout=<span class="string">"1000"</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> </span><br><span class="line">		   <span class="string">"1110011"</span> <span class="keyword">when</span> qout=<span class="string">"1000"</span> <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">		   <span class="string">"0000000"</span> ;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://md.byr.moe/uploads/upload_90a3dc418c2bb1d10f3b662a7ac491fd.png" alt=""></p>
]]></content>
