  <entry>
    <title>实验1：发光二极管走马灯电路设计与实现</title>
    <url>/2020/08/04/%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C1%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%85%89%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1%E8%B5%B0%E9%A9%AC%E7%81%AF%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h4 id="实验要求"><a href="#实验要求" class="headerlink" title="实验要求"></a>实验要求</h4><p>设计并实现一个控制 16 个发光二极管亮灭的电路，仿真验证其功能，并下载到实验板测试。</p>
<ul>
<li>单点移动模式：从左至右依次循环点亮 16 个发光二极管，每个发光二极管的点亮时间为 0.5 秒；</li>
<li>幕布式：从中间两个发光二极管开始点亮，向两边每次增加点亮 2 个发光二极管，直至点亮 16 个发光二极管；然后再从两边开始每次灭掉 2个发光二极管，直至所有发光二极管灭掉，依次往复，每个状态持续时间为 0.5 秒； </li>
<li>两个模式可用按键进行切换，要求为按键设计防抖动电路； </li>
<li>时钟频率选择 100Hz。</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h4><figure class="highlight vhdl"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">LIBRARY</span> IEEE;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">USE</span> IEEE.STD_LOGIC_1164.<span class="keyword">ALL</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">USE</span> IEEE.STD_LOGIC_UNSIGNED.<span class="keyword">ALL</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ENTITY</span> lamp <span class="keyword">IS</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">PORT</span>(clk: <span class="keyword">IN</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        reset:<span class="keyword">IN</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        change: <span class="keyword">IN</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        light: <span class="keyword">OUT</span> <span class="built_in">STD_LOGIC_VECTOR</span>(<span class="number">15</span> <span class="keyword">DOWNTO</span> <span class="number">0</span>));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">END</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">architecture</span> lamp <span class="keyword">of</span> lamp <span class="keyword">is</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">signal</span> temp:<span class="built_in">integer</span> <span class="keyword">range</span> <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">to</span> <span class="number">49</span>;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">signal</span> clk2:<span class="built_in">std_logic</span>;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">type</span> state1_type <span class="keyword">is</span>(s0,s1,s2,s3,s4,s5,s6,s7,s8,s9,s10,s11,s12,s13,s14,s15);</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">signal</span> state1: state1_type;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">type</span> state2_type <span class="keyword">is</span>(ss0,ss1,ss2,ss3,ss4,ss5,ss6,ss7,ss8,ss9,ss10,ss11,ss12,ss13,ss14,ss15);</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">signal</span> state2: state2_type;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">begin</span>   </span><br><span class="line">   divider:<span class="keyword">process</span>(clk)</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">begin</span></span><br><span class="line">           <span class="keyword">if</span>(temp=<span class="number">49</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">               temp&lt;=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="keyword">elsif</span>(clk<span class="symbol">'event</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> clk=<span class="string">'1'</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">               		temp&lt;=temp+<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="keyword">if</span>(temp&lt;<span class="number">25</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">               clk2&lt;=<span class="string">'0'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">               clk2&lt;=<span class="string">'1'</span>; </span><br><span class="line">           <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>; </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">process</span>;</span><br><span class="line">   lamp:<span class="keyword">process</span>(reset,clk2)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">begin</span></span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span>(reset=<span class="string">'1'</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">                light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000000000000000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                state1&lt;=s0;</span><br><span class="line">                state2&lt;=ss0;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">elsif</span>(clk2<span class="symbol">'event</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> clk2=<span class="string">'1'</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span>(change=<span class="string">'1'</span>)<span class="keyword">then</span> <span class="comment">--dandianmode</span></span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">case</span> state1 <span class="keyword">is</span></span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s0=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s1;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"1000000000000000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s1=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s2;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0100000000000000"</span>;  </span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s2=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s3;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0010000000000000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s3=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s4;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0001000000000000"</span>;  </span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s4=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s5;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000100000000000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s5=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s6;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000010000000000"</span>;  </span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s6=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s7;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000001000000000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s7=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s8;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000000100000000"</span>;  </span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s8=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s9;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000000010000000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s9=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s10;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000000001000000"</span>;  </span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s10=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s11;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000000000100000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s11=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s12;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000000000010000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s12=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s13;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000000000001000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s13=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s14;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000000000000100"</span>;  </span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s14=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s15;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000000000000010"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> s15=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state1&lt;=s0;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000000000000001"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">					<span class="keyword">end</span> <span class="keyword">case</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">case</span> state2 <span class="keyword">is</span></span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> ss0=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state2&lt;=ss1;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000000110000000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> ss1=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state2&lt;=ss2;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000001111000000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> ss2=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state2&lt;=ss3;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000011111100000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> ss3=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state2&lt;=ss4;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0000111111110000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> ss4=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state2&lt;=ss5;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0001111111111000"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> ss5=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state2&lt;=ss6;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0011111111111100"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> ss6=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state2&lt;=ss7;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0111111111111110"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> ss7=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state2&lt;=ss8;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"1111111111111111"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">when</span> ss8=&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        	state2&lt;=ss9;</span><br><span class="line">                    		light&lt;=<span class="string">"0111111111111110"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     